    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for Adyen API Explorer. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. Adyen's public API Explorer and openapi repository document a broad payments platform covering online checkout, recurring and tokenized payments, payouts, terminal APIs, and balance-platform operations. Public docs and specs cover payment authorization and capture flows, webhooks, BIN lookups, stores, terminal orders and assignment, terminal settings, account holders, balance accounts, and transfers. This is a strong write-capable financial workflow surface, but it does not represent asset or telemetry data. Asset data is Unsupported. Telemetry data is Unsupported. Writeback is Supported.",
